The Zeek OCSP dashboard provides insights into OCSP (Online Certificate Status Protocol) activity, which is used to check the revocation status of SSL/TLS certificates. This dashboard displays details about OCSP requests and responses, including certificate authorities, certificate status, and response times. Monitoring OCSP traffic helps ensure that SSL/TLS connections are secure and trusted, and it can reveal issues with certificate validation, such as revoked or expired certificates.
